@ChangeCastLayer,凪,1
@ChangeCastLayer,ニアB,2
@ShowMessage,凪＆花音＆ニア,凪＆花音＆妮娅
$$Voice/Story/Main/story01804/voice_story01804_104_102
嘿～～～～

